# context-blind). The only writer is the manual `migrate-to-codex` skill, which
# unlink()s + recreates (Codex-verified cli.py:452-470) — that SEVERS the
# symlink into a regular file = visible tracked diff, never a silent CLAUDE.md
# mutation. Restore with `git checkout AGENTS.md`. Do not run migrate-to-codex
